Package gate.alignment.gui

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AlignmentAction
    This interface represents an AlignmentAction.
    AlignmentView  
    DataPublisherAction
    Implementers of this interface are the resources wishing to publish data in the Alignment editor.
    FinishedAlignmentAction
    Implementers of these are called when user says that the alignment is finished.
    IteratingMethod
    This interface declares a method that needs to be implemented by the implementors of this interface.
    PreDisplayAction
    Implementers of these are called just before the pair is displayed.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AlignmentActionsManager
    Alignment actions manager that allows managing actions that should be taken on various occasions.
    AlignmentEditor
    This class provides an editor for aligning texts in a compound document.
    AlignmentFactory
    This class provides various methods that help in alignment process.
    AlignmentTask
    Alignment Task class, used for retrieving PUAPairs
    DefaultDataModel
    Implementation of Data Model used for populating tables in the Alignment Editor.
    DefaultIteratingMethod
    Default implementation of the IteratingMethod interface.
    Pair
    It represents a pair of two annotations, one from the source document and one from the target document.
    PUAPair
    A pair representing parents of unit of alignment in the source and the target language.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    IteratingMethodException
    Exception that could occur while iterating over pairs for alignment.
